!! Destroying an Orb

An Orb of Dragonkind appears fragile, but is impervious to most damage, including the attacks and breath weapons of [[dragon]]s. However, a [[disintegrate]] spell or one good hit from an [[legendary-tier|rarity]] weapon is sufficient to destroy an orb.